name: DreamCatcher
0:
”Alexa, tell Dream Catcher to remember I dreamed pigs were flying”
”Alexa, tell Dream Catcher that I dreamed I was back in high school and had a big test”
”Alexa, ask Dream Catcher what did I dream last night?”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dream catcher
des: When you wake up in the middle of the night, the last thing you want to do is turn on a light and find a pen. Utter your dream to Dream Catcher and go back to sleep. In the morning, ask "Alexa, ask Dream Catcher what I dreamed last night" for a refresher.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
